{
  "text": "In this section we determine the optimal shape within the class of sharp and smooth spindle shapes by variationally minimizing the free energy, Eq. (6), with respect to the shape parameters \u03b5 r and R c given by Eqs. (40) and [CITATION_1] . At each step in the minimization procedure, we employ our solution method of Sec. III to constrain the director field to the optimal field for the current shape parameters.",
